en 粒IC 壞左<br />\n去華強換幾舊水搞惦</blockquote><br />\n唔係啊 係會突然間無反應，依家搞到我有時電話打嚟都聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7400ca5d4fe7e978a193c724d7697e8186ede6","tid":322344,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"我有部iPhone 5C又係咁<br />\n係咁向試掃佢會向下彈 永世都落唔倒底<br />\nKeyboard左邊成日touch唔倒or touch A會touch左S or D<br />\n每次發生問題就震熄moon再unlock過部機先會正常返(一陣)<br />\n最on9係拎左兩次去apple整果陣佢就正正常常<br />\nEven換左moon都係有呢個問題發生<br />\n唔知係咪底板接口有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc42a71d85e439692dd1e59a014aecfeaac64a9","tid":322344,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"我老婆嗰部之前都係咁亂跳<br />\n<br />\nFormat 完好左幾日<br />\n<br />\n之後再format 加錢換部7"},{"pid":"94fe0bea7d03f157b1558ddcf2d2efced24dc071","tid":322344,"uid":59739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有wifi問題？ 成日detect唔到屋企/學校wifi, 打岩密碼又話密碼錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連gps都壞埋成日定錯位<br />\nGoogle過所有方法做完都唔得<br />\n<br />\nGenius Bar條友話要成塊底板換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13751d7cc375869ff40746fe180fd28e8c90bfd8","tid":322344,"uid":20688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"未夠三年"},{"pid":"3b8439d04414ca061ce7385daf881b232d702e2b","tid":322344,"uid":11677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"我都有 上個月換左mon $700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436067dc4d5a3675d8c57327f6e3079c1e82192d","tid":322344,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩出用到依家 成日LAG到無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad